In the world of entertainment, actors and singers occupy their own respected lanes. Though some stars claim to have the talent to command an audience with both their voices and dramatic skills, in reality, most are living a misguided fantasy.Luckily, we still have a few genuine "double threats" who are talented in both creative arenas.And by the looks of it, Khaya is one of them.In an Instagram clip shared by Naima Kay, Khaya is seen entertaining the crowd at Durban's Jus Jazzin restaurant and jazz lounge, with his rendition of Ringo Madlingozi's hit song Ngiyagodola.Did we mention that he also has moves for days?You have to watch his performance below!A video posted by NaimaKay SA (@naimakaysa) on Oct 30, 2016 at 10:44am PDT Find the hottest celebrity and entertainment news on TshisaLIVE or follow TshisaLIVE on Facebook and Twitter.